Class BillingInformationValidator

  • Object
    • BillingInformationValidator

  • public class BillingInformationValidator
extends Object
    BillInformation is a auxiliary class for classes that wish to manipulate a BillingInformation instance. It provides a single method update(View, BillingInformation) to update the provided BillingInformation instance.
